msgstr "La Convention sur la diversité biologique (CDB)"

#: ../../_docs/Rationale.md:24
msgid "The United Nations Convention to Combat Desertification (UNCCD)"
msgstr "La Convention des Nations Unies sur la lutte contre la désertification (UNCCD)"

