#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "The Dynamic Matrix type is similar to a [Multiple-Choice Matrix](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-guide#multiple-choice-matrix), but respondents can add and remove matrix rows."
msgstr "Le type de matrice dynamique est similaire à une [matrice à choix multiples](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-guide#multiple-choice-matrix), mais les répondants peuvent ajouter et supprimer des lignes de la matrice."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "![Dynamic Matrix](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-dynamic-rows.png \"Dynamic Matrix\")"
msgstr "![Matrice dynamique](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-dynamic-rows.png \"Matrice dynamique\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:62
msgid "Dynamic Matrix"
msgstr "Matrice dynamique"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Multiple Text**"
msgstr "**Texte multiple**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "Respondents enter their answers into multiple single-line text editors. Use the Multiple Text type for open-ended questions that require more than one short answer."
msgstr "Les répondants saisissent leurs réponses dans plusieurs éditeurs de texte sur une seule ligne. Utilisez le type Texte multiple pour les questions ouvertes qui nécessitent plusieurs réponses courtes."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "![Multiple Text](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-multiple-text.png \"Multiple Text\")"
msgstr "![Texte multiple](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-multiple-text.png \"Texte multiple\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:63
msgid "Multiple Text"
msgstr "Texte multiple"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Panel**"
msgstr "**Panneau**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "The Panel type is a container for other questions and panels. Use this type to group several questions or panels and control them all together."
msgstr "Le type Panel est un conteneur pour d’autres questions et panels. Utilisez ce type pour regrouper plusieurs questions ou panneaux et les contrôler tous ensemble."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Dynamic Panel**"
msgstr "**Panneau dynamique**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "The Dynamic Panel type is a template panel that can contain multiple questions. Respondents can add and remove panels based on the template."
msgstr "Le type Dynamic Panel est un panneau modèle qui peut contenir plusieurs questions. Les répondants peuvent ajouter et supprimer des panneaux en fonction du modèle."

