msgstr "Aperçu de la liste des services"

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Services.md:40
msgid "This option will only appear if no service listing page already exists as there can only be on instance/occurrrence of a service listing page."
msgstr "Cette option n'apparaîtra que si aucune page de liste de services n'existe déjà, car il ne peut y avoir qu'une instance/occurrence d'une page de liste de services."

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Services.md:49
msgid "Select Service List Page from the type of pages provided."
msgstr "Sélectionnez Page de liste de services parmi le type de pages fournies."

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Services.md:51
